                    <item>
                      <p>Twelve paper leaves, about 12 7/8 in. by 9 7/8, several of which are
                        stained and torn (Add. 17,224, foll. 22—33). Each page is divided into two
                        columns, of from 21 to 25 lines. The writing is good and regular, of the
                        xiiith cent., with occasional Greek vowels and other points. </p>
                    </item>
